# PS2 VMC Groups for Neutrino/NHDDL
# Based on: https://github.com/sync-on-luma/xebplus-neutrino-loader-plugin/wiki/Memory-Card-Groups
#
# Format:
#   XEBP_xxx.xx        <- Group ID header (becomes the VMC filename)
#   GAME_ID|Title      <- Title ID entry belonging to this group
#
# Cross-game groups use XEBP_100.xx naming.
# Multi-disc groups use XEBP_000.xx naming.
#
# NOTE: Groups 24 and 40 contain many games whose combined save data may
# exceed 8MB.  Consider using a 32MB image for those groups if needed.

